                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Webb</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">St. Petersburg</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-04-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 27, 1894</hi>
                        </date>. (Received April 27.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Russian minister, Washington, authorized to sign arrangement annexed to your
                    instruction of March 30. Russian Government ready to enter into
                    negotiations.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
